struct.exostring: If character is female, nothing happens

Yun initiates conversation when player enters the Sith party apartment
Dialog mission statement:
Male players can speak to Yun and through persuasion and paying credits convince him to arrange for them to get invited to a party where they can steal his keycard.
Female players can flirt with him and use persuasion to get invited to a party where they can steal his keycard.
Exit points:
1. Player at party, Yun initiates conversation, fade to black and come back with everyone drunk and passed out. Player can loot body of keycard.
2. Player bribed Yun, he leaves are to arrange party, mark party apartment on map.
3. Nothing happens
4. Nothing happens.
5. Nothing happens.
6. Player rejected, nothing else happens
7. Player rejected, nothing else happens
8. Player invited to party.
escape area, go to party house.
Fade to black, come back and everyone is passed out on the floor. Player can loot the sleeping bodies.
